data.description: Beautiful secluded lake home is designed to enjoy the gracious outdoor living spaces. The outdoor screened porch w/ fireplace is where you will enjoy eating and relaxing year round. This 4BR 5 BA unique find features 3400 heated sq ft with reclaimed pine floors, custom bookshelves and extra storage with walk in pantry. Downstairs master includes massive closet space and a deck with beautiful views. Grow your own vegetables or herbs in the irrigated multiple raised beds. Never worry about being w/o power with the large walk in storage that includes a generator. Other features: mosquito system, underground fence, dock and additional acreage available. Call today for your personal tour!
